dct_description_sm: Shows coastline surrounding Punta Icacos, Belize; depths shown by soundings. At head of title: Central America, east coast. "521." Historic Maps copy has label on verso: West Indies. Icacos Road. 521. Shows coastline off Icacos Point on the island of Trinidad; depths shown by soundings.
dct_publisher_sm: London : Published according to Act of Parliament at the Hydrographical Office of the Admiralty, April 21st. 1833.
